desc_short	-----								5089 is an open-world action RPG featuring procedural terrain, items, enemies, quests & more. This standalone expansion of 3089 takes place 2000 years later & planet Xax is crumbling... can it be saved? New content, improved visuals & more!							
developer									Phr00t's Software								
